 class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1280 1040' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-f84b72d0b64d9bf9516bd0e1720b8e09'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-f84b72d0b64d9bf9516bd0e1720b8e09)' width='1280' height='1040' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAG7ElEQVRo3uVaaU8bRxjm57TNUYgBm8PYYDs2GIzBQC41TRWlqZI0d5PmqCJFqfq5P6BVlSZVGo6k/ReVqko5EGloxH34Wu%2buD4yx/fR9Z1lYaAAbpQo2Kz2a8e7s7LzPvNeMp%2bKE5x66287hk/ar%2bKzrOo61XUag5Qx6HGfX4Rx6nWdwquN7XDr6O24EBnCrbwg3ewZxs3cI3xx%2bitv0%2b/YhxhN6Pojr/v4VXO14jK98hI4i4DOU63B1%2bdk1X//yvQFC/2ob8V6/1qazH1d8D3Gp/QFuH%2bnHhbb7uNH7GF93D6DC6ziOKncNOvxu9B71w93mRLW5EuY6E2rrDqDWcgCW%2bmqqm2C11cDfegknvxjE7WOPce/0E9z5dAB3Tw7hu9O/4e6JIXz7%2bVPcOT6IW0foAz2/Eh7heuCR%2bPjljofFoV0rL3l/1kB9iH68D3ClVRPoy7YfRXne8wO1uY/z9OwC4TLdY0H52UWvVl5opeetP4l%2br3b%2bIkipsDU40GJrRk11LSzmOtTWmNHS7IC1sQlNVhua7S2oqjognpmqq2G3OuC2t8NqaUFdjQ0WkxW1VQ2o3FuLfR%2basO8DE/ZTuf%2bjany8ZxWVe2sIelk49u8xwWxqJDTAVGmhb9WjrtGGKh%2bNz%2bzEYecpNNU74es5i%2bbmdnQ32eFtpLGZ7fA428HyeZwdcNg96Pb14eLZK2i02GGtb4G9wU0a0NoBn68dbrcbXm8bWj1u%2bP1%%2buV6ypKIiHIwIZiQpJmY2FouJukJ1Kca/5eX78srsFwpJkgS4z2Lf/b/BMofmI6iYnw0t85E3cJNHLp9FfpsAclhYWMDw8DBGR0cxNzeHpaUlZDKZHQEeSzq9gIlxMoFYVCb7SNNA5wmzhDmMj4cRDCa2hfn5BEKhJBGQpvq8oDOXy%2b049c/lshoBckzB5KSEV6/GMDLymsp/MD09RwIwS0uiLAaZTJbeJ6eqMBFBTZ/y%2bR0FvrLZJV0DYuQZU6QW726WwuGUICAYXCVgxbjy%2bfc6828lgAecSmU0289p2A6z/B5fwWByQwLe97UhAel0Zo0TXC2LGbzWln2ALK81gR1NQISCviQtUdIBSjjyKyXlN0UgL0D5BWZm4iJxKQkNiIZjImSpKmdOKfLcEUSjCvkEEPIGYAuwCUD0MTr6RvSpR4EdT0BqIUXee5GEyNAMxkX5X3MoTP1VVcHz58/JpNIlREAqJZIDvQHnyXxPj9%2brjg6bQCdAxYsXL0qTAC1D0gbO6auRgEI75hSz9AgQJpAxZElrZ74QIcqOgEgkQuExvMY0NhOkbAjQBWUBjDn8rtMA